# Comment Hygiene

- Keep comments minimal and meaningful.
- Explain *why* (intent, trade-offs, gotchas), not *what* the code obviously does.
- No decorative banners (`// =====`, `// -----`).
- No narrating obvious code (e.g. `// increment counter` above `count++`).
